131
00:06:35,629 --> 00:06:37,029
Demi...

132
00:06:37,054 --> 00:06:39,054
hubungan masa depan kita.

133
00:06:39,117 --> 00:06:40,917
Itu sebabnya saya mengatakan ini.

134
00:06:41,407 --> 00:06:42,807
Ma Ri.

135
00:06:43,807 --> 00:06:45,207
Janganlah buat begini.

136
00:06:52,338 --> 00:06:53,738
Hubungan kita.

137
00:06:58,257 --> 00:07:01,073
Jangan cakap perkara sampah
pada saya.

138
00:07:01,544 --> 00:07:03,544
Ini bermakna perang.

139
00:07:03,694 --> 00:07:06,064
Saya takkan cakap dengan orang
yang menyakitkan hati anak saya.

140
00:07:06,089 --> 00:07:09,601
Saya rasa sangat marah sekarang.

141
00:07:09,971 --> 00:07:12,172
Awak! Sekiranya awak tak pergi...

142
00:07:12,197 --> 00:07:13,689
meminta maaf pada Jenny sekarang,

143
00:07:13,713 --> 00:07:15,696
saya akan patahkan kaki awak.

144
00:07:17,446 --> 00:07:18,846
Awak juga!

145
00:07:19,965 --> 00:07:22,066
Awak juga. Sedarkan diri awak.

146
00:07:24,241 --> 00:07:25,641
Hentikan dia.

147
00:07:25,736 --> 00:07:27,755
- Dia sudah pergi..
- Ke mana?

148
00:07:28,722 --> 00:07:30,819
Dia memang samseng!

149
00:07:31,123 --> 00:07:33,553
