151
00:07:37,988 --> 00:07:39,988
Oh Tuhan.

152
00:07:44,381 --> 00:07:47,720
Min Hyuk sudah dewasa.

153
00:07:48,089 --> 00:07:49,289
Anakku.

154
00:07:49,314 --> 00:07:51,314
Bersiap-sedialah untuk festival itu.

155
00:07:51,387 --> 00:07:53,686
Ayah awak akan uruskan...

156
00:07:53,711 --> 00:07:55,240
Diamlah.

157
00:07:55,407 --> 00:07:57,717
Lihatlah wajah awak.

158
00:07:57,994 --> 00:08:00,733
Saya rasa sangat malu.

159
00:08:01,587 --> 00:08:04,587
Saya sangkakan wakil rakyat
itu sangat berkuasa, tetapi...

160
00:08:20,305 --> 00:08:21,705
Ma Ri.

161
00:08:23,001 --> 00:08:24,830
Beraninya awak membuatkan saya...

162
