935
00:52:35,830 --> 00:52:38,370
Baiklah. Pertandingan akan
dimulakan tidak lama lagi.

936
00:52:38,400 --> 00:52:40,500
Semua orang, pergi ke
dewan konsert sekarang.

937
00:52:40,520 --> 00:52:41,920
Cuba bertenang.

938
00:52:43,710 --> 00:52:45,610
Festival Seni Cheong A,
bahagian nyanyian klasik.

939
00:52:45,640 --> 00:52:48,810
Dipersilakan peserta nombor satu,
Bae Ro Na, di atas pentas.

940
00:52:55,830 --> 00:52:57,530
Awak boleh melakukan ini!

941
00:52:58,450 --> 00:53:01,050
