949
00:54:24,520 --> 00:54:25,920
Sangat sempurna.

950
00:54:25,950 --> 00:54:27,540
Dia menariknya dengan sempurna.

951
00:54:45,500 --> 00:54:47,590
Itu tidak masuk akal.

952
00:54:59,630 --> 00:55:01,500
- Bagus.
- Seterusnya adalah...

953
00:55:01,520 --> 00:55:04,420
- Terima kasih.
