1093
01:07:02,000 --> 01:07:03,400
Berhenti!

1094
01:07:10,650 --> 01:07:12,500
Awak kalah pada saya, Eun Byeol.

1095
01:07:12,980 --> 01:07:15,250
Ayah awak, Seok Hoon,

1096
01:07:15,670 --> 01:07:17,480
dan hadiah utama...

1097
01:07:17,860 --> 01:07:19,260
