01:10:23,430 --> 01:10:24,830
Ro Na!

1128
01:10:44,460 --> 01:10:46,430
Awak salah, Ro Na.

1129
01:10:47,650 --> 01:10:51,550
Saya tidak akan kehilangan
apa-apa kepada awak.

1130
01:10:53,130 --> 01:10:56,600
Bukan ayah saya, bukan Seok Hoon,

1131
01:10:57,920 --> 01:10:59,660
